<HL>
   Japanese Retailer
   Sells American Sake,
   Igniting Controversy
   ---
   Liquor Dealer Says Brewers
   Are Creating a Bottleneck
   For Imported Rice Wine
   ----
   By Yumiko Ono
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
02/28/92
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A9B
</SO>
